\newlabel{fig:io-pipeline}{{4}{11}{Image-only (IO) listener pipeline. The scene image is annotated with integer index labels at each object center, then passed to a VLM together with the speaker utterance. No textual feature descriptions are provided. The VLM outputs a posterior over object indices, which feeds the EU decision rule}{figure.caption.18}{}}
